      "author": "casperkwok",
      "description": "Loupe 1.1.2 — review-hardening & lighter build.\n\n- **Zero dynamic code**: replaced mammoth with an in-house .docx reader (fflate unzip + native DOMParser + DOM APIs). Removes all eval / new Function / dynamic <script> usage and a vulnerable transitive dependency.\n- **Bundle size cut by ~60%** (857 KB -> 352 KB).\n- Description no longer contains the word Obsidian; authorUrl points to author profile.\n- Removed !important from styles; dropped the builtin-modules dev dependency.\n\nFormats unchanged: HTML, Excel (xlsx/xls/xlsm/xlsb/ods), CSV/TSV, Word (docx), JSON, and 50+ code & config formats.",
